column5: You sure you're playin with a full scale there Paul??  How's that habit kicking going...
People are starting to agrivate the crap outa me. My dogs keep staring at me, and i smell like an ashtray when i wake up in the morning. other than that !!!! FINE ok !!!!
Stick with it Paul, the first 2 weeks are the worst.The next 2 weeks are living hell.
It's only a habit.... rabbit.... get it
